description: This skill allows the user to spell out a word or a list of words in either Morse Code or Telephony(Using NATO phonetic alphabet)
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask The General to say Hello in Morse Code
Alexa, ask The General to say Hello in Telephony
Alexa, ask The General to say The Weather Looks Nice in Telephony
name: The General
shortDescription: Spell Words in telephony or Morse Code
